Metadata: Novel sponge-derived amino acids. 11. The entire absolute stereochemistry of the bengamides

The complete stereochemistry of bengamides A and B, a new category of amino acid derivatives from a choristid sponge, can be assigned as 5R,6S,7R,8R,10Sâ€‹, and 13S. This absolute stereochemistry can also be extended to other bengamide derivatives C, D, E, and F, and isobengamide E.
